(235, '中', '她对男朋友的要求是：高等收入、中等长相、低等智商。', 'tā duì nánpéngyou de yāoqiú shì ：gāoděng shōurù 、zhōngděng zhǎngxiàng 、dīděng zhìshāng 。', 'Her requirements of her boyfriend are: high income, average looking and low IQ.', 'https://s3contents.chinesepod.com/extra/QW0466/6a4c8ab0b4a85193a52f3157d0a32e09b63b75bc/mp3/64/chinesepod_8339_dialogue_80132_prototype_1606649960.mp3', 'Upper-Intermediate', '2022-12-21 03:31:45', '2022-12-21 03:31:45'),
